                            <Cell row="1" colspan="2" textAlign="center" font="normal 700 28px/1.2999999523162842 &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;,&quot;NotoSansKR-Regular&quot;,&quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;,&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;MS PGothic&quot;" text="총점"/>
